body.description: Deck the halls with Bim Bam Boo Holiday Tubular Tissues! Experience the magic of bamboo as you banish dusty paper particles and wipe away sniffles. Whether you’re dashing through the snow or stuffing stockings, these travel tissues add holiday cheer to every sneeze. Tis the Season for Travel Tissues Bim Bam Boo holiday travel facial tissues are trusty companions for handling messes. And they’re as snug as a warm blanket on a snowy day. Slide them into cup holders and diaper bags effortlessly. Bye-bye bulky tissue boxes— it's time to roll in the cheer with our tubes!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not bad. Clever design for putting in cup holders
reviews.reviewText: This review is for: Festive Winter Kid-Friendly Facial Tissues for Travel and To-Go, Fits in Cupholder and made of BambooThis is a handy little pack of three. The cylindrical containers are pretty sturdy. They're not going to get crushed easily. You could throw the spares in your glove compartment or in the trunk and they're not going to get smashed easily.The design is clever and convenient for putting in cupholders, especially when someone in the car is sick or has allergies.It would be nice if there were refills sold.The tissues are okay. They are not as nice as the tissue that most of us are accustomed to. They are a bit on the thin and small side. They are bamboo, so there is going to be a difference. They're not bad, they're just not quite as good as what most people have been using over the years.A three pack for the current price of about 10 bucks is not too bad, in my opinion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are So Cute!
reviews.reviewText: This three pack of cup holder tissues is great for the back seat cup holders for your kids and back seat passengers. They fit in virtually all cup holders, even the ones in your door! They come in three cute designs and make it easy to reach and have tissues on hand. I do wish they came with more than 30 tissues per box, but this is a great start!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very Cute Cup Holder Tissues - Very Thin and Tiny Sheets of Tissue Paper
reviews.reviewText: The Bim Bam Boom Festive Winter Kid-Friendly Facial Tissues is a cute and adorably designed cylinder of tissues to keep in the car. The little cardboard containers fit in cupholders and side door cupholders perfectly and feature adorable prints on the outside. While I love the look of the containers, I can't say I love the tissues. The tissues feel like the tissues you get on airplanes - thin, slightly rough, and tears easily - and the sheets are smaller than standard tissue paper. I found that when folding in half and blowing my nose, I still felt like I got snot on my fingers. Overall, these are very cute, but I'd rather have a box of tissues in my car with standard-sized sheets that are thicker.
